{"tid":1656107,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【申請免拆獲批】TVBuddy省到立立令 繼續屹立無綫大門","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T12:50:59.000Z","uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e53cb65c7fdf1458cc4aae11e84eb3ca3e84873","tid":1656107,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"無綫電視將代表公司的吉祥物TVBuddy公仔，豎立於將軍澳工業區電視廣播城的入口天台上。早前被揭發屬僭建物，屋宇署收到投訴後，已向有關業主發出警告信，繼昨日下午傳出無綫疑似拆TVBuddy後，《蘋果》實地視察，發現工作人員只是為TVBuddy清潔和打蠟。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午《蘋果》收到消息指TVBuddy被肢解拆掉頭頂天線，當記者去到電視城門口時，發現沒有天線的TVBuddy被3位工作人員包圍，其中兩位戴上口罩的工作人員正利用噴槍為TVBuddy重新上色，似乎是為下月19日的台慶作翻新工程。<br />\n<br />\n今日有消息指出，TVBuddy可以留低免清拆，事關無綫向屋宇署申請，於TVBuddy加建鐵架穩固，並獲屋宇署批准，故可避過清拆命運。"},{"pid":"0908f7f36ca49a02c5d91ee772ef1abe9f78a2c1","tid":1656107,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"幫下佢手"},{"pid":"8f3e214569d43649b58e98aee2aff9a996f75d74","tid":1656107,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n擺明挑機"},{"pid":"f6481f9353f5fc4f87a47cc8f65353be40721d5d","tid":1656107,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"投訴到拆到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c003c014e1a39b1bc96724fc647428a613b22e51","tid":1656107,"uid":30063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"